description:
The QQOQQ is the Defiance in Ignorance Prize, awarded for the dumbest question asked in the arrogant belief that there is no possible answer. 

Winning video can be found at: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=poCvPV9uMYg. However, the identity of the mystery man behind the redneck curtain turns out to be a YouTuber called qwertyfshag. He took down his original video, but it was reposted by Moouan.
   qwertyfshag's channel can be found at:  http://www.youtube.com/user/qwertyfshag

Andy's response to this video can be found at 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EShr_p9pJDU
